Telkom has announced FreeMe contract prices for the Samsung Galaxy S9 and Galaxy S9 Plus. Pre-orders are available on the Telkom website, and the devices are set to launch on its network from 16 March. Clients who successfully pre-order a device will receive a R500 Samsung accessory voucher and six months of free Samsung Mobile Care cover, said Telkom. “Our FreeMe deals offer 50 free SMS messages per day, free calls to over 6 million Telkom numbers, free Wi-Fi, and free instant messaging data,” said Telkom. Telkom’s LIT Music and LIT Video value-added services will also be included with qualifying plans. The FreeMe contract deals are listed below.